00:13:16.940 --> 00:13:18.270
It's so pretty!

00:13:19.660 --> 00:13:23.650
<i>Spe-chan is always honest about her feelings,</i>

00:13:23.650 --> 00:13:24.860
<i>and she's with me…</i>

00:13:28.230 --> 00:13:32.270
Suzuka-san, it's my first time
seeing fireworks this big.

00:13:32.270 --> 00:13:33.490
It's so much fun.

00:13:34.510 --> 00:13:35.310
Yeah.

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:42.000
{\an6}Umamusume

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:42.000
{\an6}Pretty Derby

00:13:43.270 --> 00:13:44.760
I know it's just after the Fan Festival,

00:13:45.190 --> 00:13:46.620
but we can't let our guard down.

00:13:46.620 --> 00:13:47.630
Right!

00:13:54.090 --> 00:13:55.350
Grass!

00:14:00.610 --> 00:14:02.010
What is it?

00:14:02.010 --> 00:14:04.220
I said we'd make only minor changes.

00:14:04.220 --> 00:14:06.140
Why are you doing things that
aren't part of the plan?

00:14:06.590 --> 00:14:07.860
It's okay.

00:14:07.860 --> 00:14:09.060
I'm not tired yet…

00:14:09.060 --> 00:14:10.980
I am the one who'll decide that!

00:14:12.290 --> 00:14:14.260
I want to win, no matter what,

00:14:14.260 --> 00:14:15.790
in the Mainichi Okan.

00:14:15.790 --> 00:14:17.530
At this slow rate…

00:14:17.530 --> 00:14:19.420
You don't have to rush.

00:14:20.070 --> 00:14:22.100
You don't have to worry about my injury.

00:14:22.100 --> 00:14:23.580
I'm completely healed up.

00:14:23.580 --> 00:14:26.300
But you're far from being ready to race.

00:14:27.270 --> 00:14:29.290
The Mainichi Okan will be important,

00:14:29.290 --> 00:14:32.390
but your goal should be to win a G-I race.

00:14:33.910 --> 00:14:34.810
But…

00:14:34.810 --> 00:14:36.850
This is all for your sake.

00:14:48.730 --> 00:14:50.570
It's from the customer over there.

00:14:54.410 --> 00:14:56.200
I'll take the check.

00:14:56.200 --> 00:14:57.000
Hey!

00:15:00.030 --> 00:15:01.220
I see…

00:15:01.820 --> 00:15:05.750
You're working harder than
anyone for Grass Wonder.

00:15:06.780 --> 00:15:10.700
You should know just how
bad an injury can be.

00:15:10.700 --> 00:15:12.140
Yeah.

00:15:12.900 --> 00:15:17.080
If a horse girl who's running
seventy kilometers an hour falls…

00:15:17.080 --> 00:15:19.950
And the girl isn't the only one hurt by it.

00:15:21.150 --> 00:15:24.520
Anyway, Spica's doing well right now.

00:15:24.520 --> 00:15:27.400
Still letting them do whatever they please?

00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:31.390
It's best to let them feel good running.

00:15:31.390 --> 00:15:33.850
I wonder why you act so confident.

00:15:33.850 --> 00:15:35.750
The same goes for you.

00:15:38.700 --> 00:15:40.390
Anyway, Hana-san.

00:15:41.940 --> 00:15:43.330
I have something important to say.

00:15:44.180 --> 00:15:46.090
Wh-What is it?

00:15:47.410 --> 00:15:48.090
Just for tonight…

00:15:49.550 --> 00:15:51.130
You think you could get this for me?

00:15:57.670 --> 00:15:58.640
<i>Mom,</i>

00:15:59.470 --> 00:16:02.140
<i>Suzuka-san is even more excited than usual.</i>

00:16:02.670 --> 00:16:06.580
<i>I want everyone to do well
in the Mainichi Okan.</i>

00:16:09.100 --> 00:16:10.770
<i>This year's Mainichi Okan is</i>

00:16:10.770 --> 00:16:13.990
<i>attracting far more spectators
than you would expect for a G-II race.</i>

00:16:13.990 --> 00:16:17.690
Silence Suzuka from Team Spica
is the one to keep an eye on.

00:16:17.690 --> 00:16:19.910
Spica's doing well right now.

00:16:19.910 --> 00:16:22.250
Team Rigil's sure to put on a good show, too.

00:16:22.900 --> 00:16:25.060
Hey, the race is going to begin.

00:16:25.060 --> 00:16:26.750
We'll make it with time to spare.

00:16:27.060 --> 00:16:29.710
It's going to be
Rigil versus Spica in this race.

00:16:29.710 --> 00:16:32.050
Spica's pretty strong right now.

00:16:32.050 --> 00:16:33.840
Look at all this merch I bought!

00:16:34.180 --> 00:16:37.800
Everyone's talking about Spica,
and we're coming through!

00:16:38.300 --> 00:16:41.290
What plan did you give Suzuka-senpai?

00:16:41.290 --> 00:16:42.390
Nothing, really.

00:16:42.390 --> 00:16:43.520
Again?

00:16:44.290 --> 00:16:47.870
It's best to let her run the way she wants.

00:16:56.610 --> 00:16:59.320
Well, we know how this is going to turn out.

00:16:59.320 --> 00:17:01.860
The question is whether
or not the two from Rigil

00:17:01.860 --> 00:17:03.070
can keep up with Silence Suzuka.

00:17:03.070 --> 00:17:04.500
That's right.

00:17:04.500 --> 00:17:06.070
<i>It's been ten months, and she's back!</i>

00:17:06.070 --> 00:17:07.550
<i>The undefeated junior champion!</i>

00:17:07.550 --> 00:17:09.250
<i>It's Grass Wonder!</i>

00:17:09.250 --> 00:17:11.310
<i>I've worked for this day.</i>

00:17:11.310 --> 00:17:12.760
<i>I don't want to lose.</i>

00:17:12.760 --> 00:17:14.060
<i>She's won all of her races.</i>

00:17:14.060 --> 00:17:15.920
<i>She's got her eye on the global stage.</i>

00:17:15.920 --> 00:17:17.020
<i>It's El Condor Pasa!</i>

00:17:17.020 --> 00:17:18.640
Let's do this!

00:17:19.270 --> 00:17:22.020
<i>Will she show us her
graceful speed again today?</i>

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:23.390
<i>It's Silence Suzuka!</i>

00:17:24.110 --> 00:17:27.050
<i>She looks like she's here to fight this time.</i>

00:17:29.070 --> 00:17:31.480
<i>Who knows who'll win in this lineup?</i>

00:17:31.480 --> 00:17:33.150
<i>It's time for the Mainichi Okan!</i>

00:17:33.780 --> 00:17:35.400
<i>Here we go!</i>

00:17:37.410 --> 00:17:39.630
<i>Did Grass Wonder get a late start?</i>

00:17:39.630 --> 00:17:41.030
<i>She's remaining calm, though.</i>

00:17:41.590 --> 00:17:43.290
<i>I still have time to make my move.</i>

00:17:43.680 --> 00:17:46.290
<i>And Silence Suzuka, of course,
makes it to the front.</i>

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:49.130
<i>She's followed by Nice Nature
and Eishin Flash—</i>

00:17:49.130 --> 00:17:50.380
<i>They're after Silence Suzuka.</i>

00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:52.300
<i>El Condor Pasa is following behind.</i>

00:17:52.300 --> 00:17:54.460
<i>When will she make her move?!</i>

00:17:55.230 --> 00:17:57.430
<i>Silence Suzuka is staying
five horse lengths in the lead.</i>

00:17:58.100 --> 00:18:00.500
<i>Suzuka isn't that far ahead.</i>

00:18:00.500 --> 00:18:02.390
<i>We can do this, El, Grass.</i>

00:18:04.470 --> 00:18:06.730
That's the spirit.

00:18:06.730 --> 00:18:08.550
Spe-chan, what's wrong?

00:18:08.550 --> 00:18:10.400
I want to see what happens,
but I'm afraid to watch.

00:18:10.400 --> 00:18:13.050
<i>Grass Wonder is gaining from the outside!</i>

00:18:13.050 --> 00:18:15.240
<i>They're making the third turn.</i>

00:18:18.050 --> 00:18:19.570
<i>All right. This is the spot.</i>

00:18:20.950 --> 00:18:23.590
<i>Grass Wonder is catching
up to Silence Suzuka!</i>

00:18:23.590 --> 00:18:24.910
<i>Will she be able to catch her?</i>

00:18:24.910 --> 00:18:27.000
<i>I'm going to catch up!</i>

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:27.520
<i>This is it!</i>

00:18:27.520 --> 00:18:29.080
<i>Nice Nature is catching up!</i>

00:18:29.080 --> 00:18:31.370
<i>I'm going to use this chance, too, then!</i>

00:18:31.370 --> 00:18:33.210
<i>Eishin Flash is closing the gap, too!</i>

00:18:33.210 --> 00:18:34.960
<i>I can do this!</i>

00:18:34.960 --> 00:18:36.090
<i>This is it!</i>

00:18:37.290 --> 00:18:39.920
<i>El Condor Pasa is making her move now, too!</i>

00:18:39.920 --> 00:18:41.930
<i>Right at the end!</i>

00:18:42.700 --> 00:18:44.700
<i>And now for the final dash!</i>

00:18:45.210 --> 00:18:47.670
<i>They're trying to catch up to
Silence Suzuka at this point.</i>

00:18:54.300 --> 00:18:56.110
<i>I can't move up…</i>

00:18:56.860 --> 00:18:58.110
<i>I can't catch her.</i>

00:18:58.110 --> 00:19:00.950
<i>Grass Wonder is falling back!</i>

00:19:08.460 --> 00:19:10.210
<i>She's world class.</i>

00:19:11.070 --> 00:19:11.950
<i>But!</i>

00:19:11.950 --> 00:19:14.140
<i>I'm world class, too!</i>

00:19:17.170 --> 00:19:18.010
Go!

00:19:18.400 --> 00:19:21.490
<i>El Condor Pasa is catching up!</i>

00:19:24.660 --> 00:19:27.030
<i>No, it's not enough…</i>

00:19:27.030 --> 00:19:30.700
<i>It's not enough to catch up
to Silence Suzuka, though!</i>

00:19:30.700 --> 00:19:31.970
<i>I should be able to win!</i>

00:19:31.970 --> 00:19:34.360
<i>I'm going to win and get
onto the world stage!</i>

00:19:35.250 --> 00:19:37.400
I'm going to win here!

00:19:40.380 --> 00:19:44.410
<i>But Silence Suzuka is maintaining her lead!</i>

00:19:44.990 --> 00:19:47.310
<i>Silence Suzuka is staying ahead!</i>

00:19:47.310 --> 00:19:48.530
<i>Why…</i>

00:19:49.160 --> 00:19:51.160
<i>Why can't I catch up to her?</i>

00:19:51.540 --> 00:19:53.940
<i>No one has caught up to Silence Suzuka!</i>

00:19:53.940 --> 00:19:55.920
<i>What an amazing horse girl!</i>

00:19:59.070 --> 00:20:00.970
Go!

00:20:00.970 --> 00:20:02.660
Run!

00:20:02.660 --> 00:20:03.890
Suzuka-san!

00:20:06.890 --> 00:20:09.470
The horse girl with speed from
another dimension, Silence Suzuka.

00:20:09.820 --> 00:20:12.560
She's come in first!

00:20:19.570 --> 00:20:21.390
Suzuka-san!

00:20:28.390 --> 00:20:29.700
Suzuka-san?

00:20:30.050 --> 00:20:33.870
Maybe she didn't even notice
she passed the finish line…

00:20:42.690 --> 00:20:44.880
Thank you, everyone.

00:20:46.300 --> 00:20:48.890
Thank you, Spe-chan.

00:20:53.030 --> 00:20:54.260
<i>I lost…</i>

00:20:54.260 --> 00:20:57.350
<i>For the first time.</i>

00:21:09.450 --> 00:21:11.350
I'm sorry.

00:21:20.290 --> 00:21:21.140
It's fine.

00:21:21.550 --> 00:21:22.380
It's <i>fine</i>.

00:21:23.420 --> 00:21:26.880
You just have to peak during your next G-1.

00:21:30.350 --> 00:21:33.350
I thought I had a chance at winning this one.

00:21:33.350 --> 00:21:37.070
How about we go train again
so we can win the next one?

00:21:37.070 --> 00:21:40.070
Oh, I have to do the Winning Concert.

00:21:40.070 --> 00:21:41.110
You're so lucky.

00:21:42.710 --> 00:21:45.570
Let's thank everyone for
their support up there.

00:21:50.850 --> 00:21:53.080
She's world class…

00:21:53.900 --> 00:21:56.460
But I'm getting my revenge in the Tennoushou.

00:22:05.030 --> 00:22:10.720
{\an8}Pretty Derby Channel

00:22:05.410 --> 00:22:07.900
<i>Silence Suzuka has come in first.</i>

00:22:07.900 --> 00:22:10.720
<i>No one can stop Spica!</i>

00:22:12.270 --> 00:22:13.940
You're not going to keep winning.

00:22:13.940 --> 00:22:16.350
Rigil's going to win in the end.

00:22:16.350 --> 00:22:18.610
We did it!

00:22:19.480 --> 00:22:21.890
We won!

00:22:22.860 --> 00:22:23.970
Shut up!

00:22:25.700 --> 00:22:28.770
In a dash, in a flash,
just a little more now,

00:22:28.770 --> 00:22:31.480
each new race like a dream neverending

00:22:31.480 --> 00:22:34.290
Every one of us will blaze a
trail aimed right for the stars

00:22:34.290 --> 00:22:39.460
Together we'll run! Let's
go! Our starting gate!

00:22:48.590 --> 00:22:53.920
With curiosity in hand, go tug
on tomorrow's tail and say hello

00:22:53.920 --> 00:22:58.920
It's right there, so go on and close
the gap now (Right here and now!)

00:22:59.630 --> 00:23:05.010
Can't play by the rules they tell
you! Gotta learn it all by experience!

00:23:05.010 --> 00:23:09.950
If we just plan to run for the
end, everything will turn out okay!

00:23:10.110 --> 00:23:13.980
Can't get me down,
hesitate, or go too slowly!

00:23:15.730 --> 00:23:19.700
We know that deep in our hearts is a song

00:23:19.780 --> 00:23:22.920
that sings "give it your all"! Make it shine!

00:23:23.500 --> 00:23:26.720
In a dash, in a flash, just a
little more now, (Dash! Dash!)

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:29.470
every step like the wind
neverending (Zoom! Zoom!)

00:23:29.470 --> 00:23:32.370
A twinkling star that we wear
on our sleeves (But only one!)

00:23:32.370 --> 00:23:34.670
Let's let our hearts race
together as one! (Grow up! Shine!)

00:23:34.670 --> 00:23:37.800
One more step, one more push,
just a little more now, (Dash! Dash!)

00:23:37.800 --> 00:23:40.450
each new race like a dream
neverending (Zoom! Zoom!)

00:23:40.450 --> 00:23:43.300
Every one of us will see
our path to the very end!

00:23:43.300 --> 00:23:49.030
Let's run now, everyone!
Let's go! Our starting gate!

